Package: dndsR
Type: Package
Title: dN/dS Pipeline Utilities for Comparative Genomics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nick", family = "Johnson", 
           email = "john7932@msu.edu", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Utilities to extract CDS and proteins from FASTA/GFF, 
    orchestrate ortholog discovery, and run dN/dS analyses at scale. 
    Includes helpers for batch comparisons, annotation joins, and QC.
